<ul style="color:#94a3b8;line-height:2;padding-left:24px">
  <li>Precise square footage and pitch calculations for accurate replacement quotes</li>
  <li>Edge condition analysis — drip edge and fascia board deterioration</li>
  <li>Ridge and hip line integrity from satellite imagery</li>
  <li>Waste factor calculations tailored to your roof''s geometry</li>
  <li>Comparison benchmarks against similar Orlando-area properties</li>
</ul>

